  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to GNOME System Monitor</title>

    <para>
      The <application>GNOME System Monitor</application> package contains
      <application>GNOME</application>'s replacement for
      <command>gtop</command>.
    </para>

    &lfs91_checked;

